title: Create Biblatex Preamble — .PreambleBiblatex
text: path Character string. Path *.bib files. style Character string. "apa" "reading". sortcites Logical. Sort citations. sorting Character string. "nty" sort name, title, year; "nyt" sort name, year, title; "nyvt" sort name, year, volume, title; "anyt " sort alphabetic label, name, year, title; "anyvt" sort alphabetic label, name, year, volume, title; "ydnt" sort year (descending), name, title; "none" entries processed citation order. map Logical. Null mapping addendum, note, annotation.
